<H3> <TI>   Government Condemns Shelling of Sarajevo Market </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0602163694 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 1600 
GMT 6 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0602163694 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Radio Algiers Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A spokesman for the Ministry of Foreign Affairs 
announced in a statement today that Algeria strongly condemned 
the shelling of the central market in Sarajevo and was making an 
urgent appeal to the international community to translate all 
the resolutions of the UN Security Council into action 
immediately. 

</TEXT>

