<H3> <TI>   Qaddumi Urges U.S., Russia To Pressure Israel </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  JN0602193894 Paris Radio Monte Carlo in Arabic 1900 GMT 6 
Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0602193894 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris Radio Monte Carlo </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Faruq Qaddumi, head of the PLO Political Department, 
has called on Russia and the United States, the cosponsors of 
the Middle East process, to pressure Israel to expeditiously 
withdraw from Gaza and Jericho. 
  In his statement, Qaddumi said that Israeli behavior 
definitely proves that Israeli Prime Minister Yitzhaq Rabin is 
trying to avoid withdrawing the Israeli forces under security 
pretexts that are unacceptable and not in line with reality and 
facts. 

</TEXT>

