<H3> <TI>   Trial of Bush Plot Suspects Resumes Hearings </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0502111494 Kuwait KUNA in Arabic 1021 GMT 5 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0502111494 </F>
<F P=104>  Kuwait KUNA </F>


