<F P=102> NC0702094494 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 0900 GMT 7 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0702094494 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] An agent force [South Lebanese Army] raked both 
sides of the road between the al-Khiyam junction and al-Hasbani 
Bridge. Israeli forces stationed in the 'Ayn Qinya hills opened 
heavy machine-gun fire on Mimis Bridge and the surrounding woods 
for 20 minutes at dawn today. They fired flares over the area, 
causing fires in groves nearby. The Israeli artillery bombarded 
the al- Rayhan woods in the Jazzin area this morning and columns 
of smoke could be seen billowing in the area. 
  Israeli military aircraft overflew the south, concentrating 
on al-Nabatiyah and Iqlim al-Tuffah, before midnight. 

