<F P=103> JN0602184494 </F>
<F P=104>  Damascus SANA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] Damascus, 6 Feb (SANA)--His Majesty King Husayn 
Bin-Talal of the Hashemite Kingdom of Jordan arrived in Damascus 
at 1215 today. President Hafiz al-Asad led those who received 
him at the airport. [passage omitted] 
  After his majesty the king shook hands with the ministers 
and 
staff of the Jordanian Embassy in Damascus, the president and 
his guest headed in an official motorcade for the People's 
Palace where they held a meeting. [passage omitted] 
  His Majesty King Husayn offered his condolences to the 
