covered the Middle East peace process in light of the talks 
between President Hafiz al-Asad and U.S. President Bill Clinton 
in Geneva and the talks between His Majesty King Husayn and 
President Clinton in Washington, and also in light of the recent 
Arab-Israeli talks in Washington. Discussion also dealt with 
the situation in the Arab arena. 

