<F P=103> NC0702191894 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi Islamic Revolution 
in Arabic 1430 GMT 7 Feb 94 </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105>Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The regime has continued its brutal oppressive acts 
against the Iraqi people, seeking to destroy the marshlands in 
southern Iraq. The regime's artillery shelled the regions of 
(Bahilah) Nahr Salih, Abu-Saddah, (Muray'an) (al-Mifrakh), and 
