<H3> <TI>   Poll: Ramon Best for Premier After Rabin, Peres </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA0402115494 Tel Aviv YEDI'OT AHARONOT in Hebrew 4 Feb 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> TA0402115494 </F>
<F P=104>  Tel Aviv YEDI'OT AHARONOT </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Hebrew </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> ["Public opinion poll conducted for YEDI'OT AHARONOT by the </F>
