<H3> <TI>   Mubarak, Musa Mediate PLO-Israeli Talks in Cairo </TI></H3>
<H4>   Mubarak Receives 'Arafat, Peres </H4>
<F P=102> NC0802175894 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1724 GMT 8 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0802175894 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 8 Feb (MENA)--President Muhammad Husni 
Mubarak held a meeting this evening at the Presidential Palace 
attended by Palestinian President Yasir 'Arafat and Israeli 
Foreign Minister Shim'on Peres. 
  President Mubarak met before that with 'Arafat and Peres 
separately. 

</TEXT>

