Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 8 Feb (MENA)--The Sudanese opposition 
al-Ummah Party issued a statement in Cairo today holding the 
Sudanese Government fully responsible for opening the country's 
territory to terrorists and noting, in this connection, the 
Sudanese Foreign Ministry's decision to grant citizenship to 
members of all Islamic groups. 
