<H3> <TI>   Jordanian Ambassador Robbed by Highwaymen </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC0802162194 (Clandestine) Voice of the People of Kurdistan 
in Arabic 1500 GMT 8 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC0802162194 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of the People of Kurdistan 
