<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105>Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A responsible source in the city of al-Ramadi told 
us that while the Jordanian ambassador was travelling in his 
private car to Baghdad in mid-December 1993, he was stopped by a 
number of unknown gunmen on the highway between Baghdad and 
al-Ramadi. He was robbed of all his personal belongings and 
